Fourth Department,

June, 1999

(June 18, 1999) Teresa Castellani, Respondent, v Susann Bagdasarian, Appellant. (Appeal No. 1.) [691 NYS2d 809]

—Appeal unanimously dismissed without costs (see, Smith v Catholic Med. Ctr., 155 AD2d 435; see also, CPLR 5501 [a] [1], [2]). (Appeal from Order *932of Supreme Court, Erie County, Cosgrove, J. — Set Aside Verdict.) Present — Denman, P. J., Hayes, Wisner, Hurlbutt and Callahan, JJ.
